OL,6,FHeritage is looking for relatives of
OL,7,Fheroes from the ahead of the roll-out
OL,8,Fof Stolperstein memorial stones across
OL,9,Fthe Island.
OL,11,FThe organisation has tracked down
OL,12,Frelatives for half of the 20 people
OL,13,Fwho will be honoured by the stones,
OL,14,Fbut is struggling to find family for
OL,15,Fthe remaining 10.
OL,17,FStolpersteines, translating to
OL,18,F'stumble stones', are cobblestones
OL,19,Fembedded into pavements to commemorate
OL,20,Fvictims and survivors of Nazism.
