OL,6,FThere are now more than 100,000
OL,7,FStolpersteine laid across mainland
OL,8,FEurope.
OL,10,FEach brass cap is handmade by German
OL,11,Fartist Gunter Demnig, who will visit
OL,12,Fthe Channel Islands in July to install
OL,13,Fsome of the 20 stones in Jersey and ,
OL,14,Fwith schools and community groups
OL,15,Fexpected to install the remainder.
OL,17,FChris Addy from Jersey Heritage said:
OL,18,F"The support we have received so far
OL,19,Ffor the Stolpersteine project has been
OL,20,Fwonderful.
