OL,6,F"The 20 Stolpersteine in Jersey will
OL,7,Fprovide a moving commemoration for
OL,8,Fsurvivors of the Occupation.
OL,10,F"We hope there might be an opportunity
OL,11,Fin the future to add further stones to
OL,12,Fremember people who lived through
OL,13,Fthese difficult years."
OL,15,FIris Prigent's late husband, Gordon,
OL,16,Fwill be commemorated after being
OL,17,Fconscripted to during Jersey's
OL,18,FOccupation.
