OL,6,FIris explained: "My husband Gordon
OL,7,Fsuffered greatly as a result of being
OL,8,Fsent to Alderney for refusing to work
OL,9,Ffor the Occupiers.
OL,11,F"This experience affected him for the
OL,12,Frest of his life.
OL,14,F"Gordon would have been happy to think
OL,15,Fthat he and many others who suffered
OL,16,Fduring the German Occupation are being
OL,17,Fremembered."
